{"tid":1354330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[\t保皇黨認證] 黃國健：中聯辦外宣布要成立臨時立法會，光復香港屬於嚴重政治事件","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:09.000Z","uid":36592,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa5ccb142aec184c6222143ba8aa1530357c717","tid":1354330,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"另一行會成員、工聯會副會長黃國健表示，昨晚發生了兩件令人痛心的事，包括中聯辦受衝擊，有人在中聯辦門外宣布要成立臨時立法會，光復香港等港獨言辭，屬於嚴重政治事件。他重申，香港是中國不可分割的領土，這是不能改變的。黃國健亦譴責於元朗發生的暴力事件，但他稱凡事「有果必有因」，而「因」就是現今社會上愈來愈多「火頭」，由6月9日開始，有人衝擊立法會，而每次遊行之後都有暴力衝擊事件發生，亦有人在各個地區發起衝擊，認為這一連串暴力事件令不少人「形成爆炸性情緒，係好容易著火」。 <br />\n<br />\n擇錄自眾新聞報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22282/%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE-22282/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%A5%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%9C%E5%BF%85%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%A0%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F22282%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE-22282%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%25A5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%25BF%2585%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259B%25A0%25E3%2580%258D&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=02dc3332\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22282/%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE-22282/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%A5%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8